<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>as a last resort • in the last resort</xh5><p> <i>as a last resort—</i>as a last means; when everything else has been tried and failed: The imprisonment of a child should be used only <u>as a last resort</u>.</p><p> <i>in the last resort—</i>ultimately; in the end: He was worried about his production figures. <u>In the last resort</u> it was the human factor that counted.</p> </entry>
